title: Motley Crue - Wilkes Barre, PA - November 3, 1998
description:
Not my camera work (although I did record this concert as well - this is better than mine).  Great Motley show from the Greatest Hits Tour which Tommy would later abandon and Randy Castillo would take over.   But for this show it was all original members.  I've included a cover for you -- please don't hit and run, I will only seed the torrent for a few days, and it's up to the community to keep it alive.

Dr. Feelgood 
Girls, Girls, Girls 
Enslaved
